Package com.corvolution.cm2.fileadapter

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BinaryFileAdapter
    This class represents adapter for binary files.Classes extending this class must call parent constructor with a path to binary file for creating their instances.
    ConfigFile
    This class represents configuration file of sensor.When sensor connected instance of this class is created and initialized.
    CustomFile
    This class represents custom file of sensor.
    InfoFile
    This class represents Info file of sensor.
    StatusFile
    This class represents status file of sensor.
    TextFileAdapter
    This class represents adapter for text files.Classes extending this class must call parent constructor with a path to text file for creating their instances.
    TimeSyncFile
    This class represents timeSync file of sensor.
